            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1655808129423-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>blanched peas</strong> and <strong>rocket </strong>to a colander and pour <strong>cold water</strong> all over them to refresh them</p><p>Pat them dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine the <strong>Dijon mustard</strong>,<strong> </strong>the juice of the <strong>remaining lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>in a small bowl</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1655808132574-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1655808132574-x400.jpg",
